title: GET_VEHICLE_TOP_SPEED_MODIFIER
content:
0x998B7FEE// GetVehicleTopSpeedModifier
float GET_VEHICLE_TOP_SPEED_MODIFIER(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The target vehicle.Returns: Returns vehicle's modified top speed.A getter for MODIFY_VEHICLE_TOP_SPEED. Returns -1.0 if a modifier is not set.
